<div class="home-page">
  <h1 class="header"> I'm Eirik, welcome to my portfolio </h1>
  <div class="container">
    <div class="card-top">
      <%=image_tag("Eirik.jpg", class: "picture") %>
      <div class="initdesc">
        <p>Having done a masters degree in history and tried my hand at carpentry
        I finally settled on software developer as my career</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="about-container">
    <div class="about-me">
      <h4>More about me</h4>
      <p>In january 2020 I left my full-time job as a carpenter to dedicate myself fully to learning coding</p>
      <p>I got started by learning from codecademy and reading books on programming, in may I started the Le Wagon web developer bootcamp in Oslo.</p>
      <hr>
    </div>
    <div class="expertise">
      <h4>TOP EXPERTISE</h4>
      <p>A Software Engineer with a primary focus on technology over a particular language: <a target="_blank" href="JamesMonksCV.pdf">Download CV</a></p>
        <div id="skills">
          <ul>
            <li>JavaScript</li>
            <li>Ruby</li>
            <li>Ruby on Rails</li>
            <li>Active record</li>
          </ul>
          <ul>
            <li>Heroku</li>
            <li>HTML/CSS</li>
            <li>Bootstrap</li>
            <li>SQL</li>
          </ul>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="social-media">
      <h3>Find me on LinkedIn & Github </h3>
      <ul class="list-inline">
        <li><a href="https://github.com/eirikslys" target="_blank">
          <i class="fab fa-github-square fa-9x social-icon"></i>
        </a></li>
        <li><a href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/eirik-lysenst%C3%B8en-394a4439/" target="_blank">
          <i class="fab fa-linkedin-in fa-9x social-icon"></i>
        </a></li>
      </ul>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="container-projects">
    <h2>Some of my former projects</h2>
    <div class="cards-projects">
      <div class="project">
        <%=image_tag("hotspots.png", class: "picture-project") %>
        <h5>Hotspots</h5>
        <p>A Airbnb clone for people who want to rent out and hire locations to film photoshoots I made with two others during my bootcamp. Written in ruby on rails with active record and hosted on heroku.</p>
        <div class="project-links">
          <%= link_to "live website", "https://hotspotslw.herokuapp.com/" %>
          <%= link_to "Github", "https://github.com/Eirikslys/hotspots" %>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="project">
        <%=image_tag("infitter.png", class: "picture-project") %>
        <h5>Infitter</h5>
        <p>An application that lets people get colour matched suggestions for outfits and take pictures of clothes in the store to see what clothes in their wardrobe they would match. Made with a team of two others in the last part of the boot camp.</p>
        <div class="project-links">
          <%= link_to "live website", "infitter.net" %>
          <%= link_to "Github", "https://github.com/Eirikslys/infitter" %>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="project">
        <%=image_tag("cocktail.png", class: "picture-project") %>
        <h5>Cocktail-site</h5>
        <p>A solo project</p>
        <div class="project-links">
          <%= link_to "coming soon", "#" %>
          <%= link_to "Github", "https://github.com/Eirikslys/rails-mister-cocktail" %>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
